Package se.cbb.jprime.apps.phylotools

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FilterInparalogues
    Simple app which takes a host tree and a guest tree as input, and outputs a guest tree with in-paralogues removed (the first encountered paralogue is kept).
    GeneTreeHomologyReader
    First script used for (i) testing that I can code in JPrIME, and (ii) reading homology event in true reconciliation file generated by prime_generateTree of PrIME C++ version
    LCAAnalysis
    Simple script for obtaining some aspects of the least-common-ancestor (LCA) induced by a set of guest tree leaves when reconciled with a host tree.
    ParsimoniousTimeEstimator
    Simple app which takes as input: a host tree S with times in Newick format a G-S map and returns the time span of the subtree of the host tree induced by the guest leaves.
    TestFilterInparalogues
    JUnit test class.
    TestLCAAnalysis
    JUnit test class.
